5012:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  ADCx ADC instance
5013:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @retval Returned value can be one of the following values:
